{"tid":2058702,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"李柱銘: 年輕時支持「港獨」, 後來轉而支持「民主回歸」","createTime":"2020-06-10T11:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T13:44:51.000Z","uid":134071,"like":19,"dislike":148,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"cec7dd3c2c4bd6cd42766c561e914f39cadb05fc","tid":2058702,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10156939883286121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffokguy%2Fposts%2F10156939883286121&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=f426ba1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10156939883286121</a><br />\n<br />\nKay Lam<br />\n4 小時 &middot;<br />\n <br />\n「民主回歸」當然係錯，但追查幾時犯上呢個錯，係比起老屈全地球犯呢個錯係更重要<br />\n<br />\n好多人走去貼 2017 年李柱銘的訪問，只睇標題卻冇睇內文，用來證明李柱銘支持民主回歸－－係，佢支持係講緊 1997-2017，唔係講緊 1982 年；1982 年佢作為專業人士訪京團時，向北京提左乜野？港獨<br />\n<br />\n羅永生話李柱銘係 1996 年時，轉而支持民主回歸，時間完全吻合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/OPjmipW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOPjmipW.jpg&h=1eb6bd4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10aeeaad1f131a04d52b2f43008e3707ab9d0ee4","tid":2058702,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86faf4982343d7aa2e014bf89c9ac0b1b0ec13f5","tid":2058702,"uid":24284,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"收編"},{"pid":"40d0e1b55fe0528948afaa03d684fa31b98d8edb","tid":2058702,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22fea6c5b5a184a9143d968e8eb69b66b5a5c56","tid":2058702,"uid":56428,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"cited