lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqesnNj5.png&h=99fa08b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外幫幫手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[1人1信] 要求記者協會對現場人士稱呼作出更正<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2052964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2052964</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"4de6285b47287252a6db8c7811cfbc36094e075d","tid":2058702,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cec7dd3c2c4bd6cd42766c561e914f39cadb05fc","tid":2058702,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10156939883286121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffokguy%2Fposts%2F10156939883286121&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=f426ba1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10156939883286121</a><br />\n<br />\nKay Lam<br />\n4 小時 &middot;<br />\n <br />\n「民主回歸」當然係錯，但追查幾時犯上呢個錯，係比起老屈全地球犯呢個錯係更重要<br />\n<br />\n好多人走去貼 2017 年李柱銘的訪問，只睇標題卻冇睇內文，用來證明李柱銘支持民主回歸－－係，佢支持係講緊 1997-2017，唔係講緊 1982 年；1982 年佢作為專業人士訪京團時，向北京提左乜野？港獨<br />\n<br />\n羅永生話李柱銘係 1996 年時，轉而支持民主回歸，時間完全吻合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/OPjmipW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOPjmipW.jpg&h=1eb6bd4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"民主回歸同獨立有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主歸位即獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be16d70a1d347e6235510196cafc4c2e38d210e","tid":2058702,"uid":123189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"佢年青時有港獨呢樣野咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似吹水wo"},{"pid":"c3545ed76c91df29c9b5bbe217bd6ea7e6755b23","tid":2058702,"uid":134071,"li